btrplace.model

Class SubModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • btrplace.model.SubModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ElementBuilder, Model, Cloneable

    public class SubModel
extends Object
implements Model
    Define a model that is a sub-model of a bigger one. The operation on a sub-model are limited to the elements that belong to the given scope.

    • Elements created in a sub-model are integrated automatically into the parent component
    • It is not allowed to attach/detach/clear views
    • It is not possible to set the attributes
    Author:
    Fabien Hermenier
